LABEL maintainer='s@muelcolvin.com'

RUN pip install --no-cache-dir aiohttp==3.7.3

ADD setup.py /
RUN pip install --no-cache-dir -e .

ADD ./docker-entrypoint.py /
ENTRYPOINT ["/docker-entrypoint.py"]
